      "span_text": "Expression of CrtR-b1 and CrtR-b2 in E. coli For expression in E. coli of carotenoid biosynthesis genes, plasmid pBCAR-T, carrying CrtE, CrtB, and CrtI from Erwinia uredovora and Lcy-b from tomato, and plasmid pDCAR, carrying the same genes but Lcy-e from tomato replaced Lcy-b, were used"
